Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.30,0:00:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新机动战记-钢弹W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.50,0:00:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.97,0:00:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.51,0:00:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.62,0:00:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱着你被淋湿的肩膀 想温暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.83,0:00:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,颤抖的指尖 彷徨地在找什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.63,0:00:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的视线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.91,0:01:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲伤变为力量的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.35,0:01:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.02,0:01:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.66,0:01:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.36,0:01:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.83,0:01:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[零式系统]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.74,0:01:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是把战况里出现的一切资料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.94,0:01:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在即时运算后\N得出的庞大预测值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.81,0:01:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直接反馈给驾驶员的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.64,0:01:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,驾驶舱系统的俗称
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.85,0:01:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，这系统甚至
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.68,0:01:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会把驾驶员赶进极端状况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.12,0:01:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,实现完美的胜利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.59,0:01:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,结果连自己的死也不在乎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.03,0:01:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.03,0:01:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在世界变得混沌的时候里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.76,0:01:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,存在了令人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.77,0:01:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成为最强兵器的机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.20,0:02:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是飞翼零式和次代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.18,0:02:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三十八话\N[莉莉娜女王诞生]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.88,0:02:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球的混乱\N招致宇宙卫星的混乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.55,0:02:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反抗罗姆斐拉财团支配体制的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.62,0:02:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星居民们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.32,0:02:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,组织起武装集团[白色獠牙]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.06,0:02:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了解放卫星站起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.63,0:02:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,面对这件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.13,0:02:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ虽然失去司令官兹巴洛夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.67,0:02:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但他们投入MD\N以武力对抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.24,0:02:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在各地，战争的火花\N开始扩散了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.02,0:02:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别正面冲向MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.02,0:02:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诱引它们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.06,0:02:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去卫星雷射炮的射程距离内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.42,0:02:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.66,0:03:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们为何要把无意义的战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.36,0:03:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,带来宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.03,0:03:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢…钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.55,0:03:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹看来在战斗空域出现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.42,0:03:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.79,0:04:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，以这艘穿梭机\N不能再接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.19,0:04:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多谢，来到这里就足够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.56,0:04:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之后我独自前去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.93,0:04:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.70,0:04:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹05的驾驶员吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.10,0:04:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他也在相信正义而战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.82,0:04:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有一部就歼灭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.39,0:04:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ的MD?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.52,0:04:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就是钢弹的力量吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.56,0:04:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抛掉武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.91,0:04:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抛掉所有武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.44,0:04:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果弱者拿起武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.11,0:04:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就会克服不了我的心而失控
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.51,0:04:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,弱者不要战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.16,0:05:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你仍然没变啊，张五飞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.66,0:05:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你记得吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.43,0:05:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们在维多利亚基地\N有一面之缘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.10,0:05:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当时那个女人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.27,0:05:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫路克蕾琪亚‧诺茵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.61,0:05:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.24,0:05:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我现在对你已经毫无怀恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.11,0:05:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和这个宇宙的广阔相比
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.31,0:05:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的屈辱根本是小事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.18,0:05:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看来不是来战斗啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.12,0:05:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想借助你的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.16,0:05:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.22,0:05:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想借助所有\N钢弹驾驶员的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.19,0:05:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我喜欢宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.93,0:05:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，我也爱地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.06,0:05:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我两方面都不想伤害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.77,0:05:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以，我才想要建立\N和平的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.50,0:05:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们钢弹驾驶员\N能了解我的心情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.07,0:05:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你肯帮助我吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.65,0:06:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王国吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.36,0:06:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，那国家灭亡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.89,0:06:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你为何还要战斗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.29,0:06:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,国家的确灭亡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.36,0:06:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.30,0:06:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王国的可贵精神仍然存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.83,0:06:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想保护那精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.80,0:06:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女人不会想到这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.94,0:06:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我要走我的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.64,0:06:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会服从任何人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.06,0:06:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪欧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.23,0:06:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起，我这边处理好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.50,0:07:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪欧，你担心那个人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.87,0:07:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他同样是钢弹的驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.21,0:07:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看见他变成那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.85,0:07:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，卫星今后会怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.78,0:07:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想过很多事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.45,0:07:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你担心什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.09,0:07:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要走自己相信的路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.09,0:07:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说那句话的是迪欧你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.89,0:07:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.09,0:07:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么，首先认真找份工作吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.23,0:07:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有新工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.07,0:07:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,资源卫星\N招募机动战士工作人员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.11,0:07:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.37,0:07:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事?希尔妲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.88,0:07:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是温拿家的资源卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.68,0:07:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,温拿家?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.48,0:07:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听闻她的家主被杀后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.58,0:07:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有工程一直被搁置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.32,0:07:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.69,0:07:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,温拿家的少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.54,0:08:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了，之后的交给…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.51,0:08:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好，卡特尔，很久不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.21,0:08:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪欧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.15,0:08:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是温拿家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.92,0:08:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拥有宏伟的大厦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.88,0:08:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这也是由你继承了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.15,0:08:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在还没
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.82,0:08:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐们正在管理所有资产
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.09,0:08:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自从我下落不明之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.33,0:08:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为成为钢弹驾驶员吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.66,0:08:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔，你去了哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.93,0:08:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去了地球，和希洛一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.30,0:08:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了思考应该做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.61,0:08:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，有答案吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.58,0:08:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战斗啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.08,0:08:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此，我来找你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.58,0:08:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球有很多仁慈的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.65,0:08:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星其实也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.82,0:08:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家想创造能和平生活的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.66,0:09:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了那目的，我想保护
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.56,0:09:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王国的完全和平主义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.46,0:09:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全和平吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.50,0:09:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的能创造那种世界吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.27,0:09:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪欧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.34,0:09:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直为了卫星而战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.21,0:09:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战斗的人我一个就够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.54,0:09:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有那种回忆的一个人就够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.68,0:09:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，卫星开始战争了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.11,0:09:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今后会有更多人死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.19,0:09:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我或许已经不能再相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.09,0:09:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们一直梦想的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.39,0:09:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和平始终是不会实现的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.30,0:09:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我曾经犯错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.03,0:09:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然我想不会被原谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.20,0:09:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我想豁出一切作出补偿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.90,0:09:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是不抹去名为和平的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.64,0:09:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为如果失去梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.54,0:09:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切就会结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.15,0:09:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.35,0:09:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.58,0:10:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,漆黑一片的未来\N或许很适合死神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.15,0:10:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪欧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.09,0:10:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里太高尚了，浑身不自在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.69,0:10:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我该回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.03,0:10:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你在找寻钢弹驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.77,0:10:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也想见那家伙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.61,0:10:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪欧!那是…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.34,0:10:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,振作点，莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.34,0:10:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你肩负起全世界的命运啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.04,0:10:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.59,0:11:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就在这里…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.61,0:11:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了，我现在就喂你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.58,0:11:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.65,0:11:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦…你是特洛瓦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.76,0:11:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.12,0:11:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.76,0:11:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你认识我吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.39,0:11:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦!你不认得我吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.67,0:11:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦!去那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.80,0:11:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…姐姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.24,0:12:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.60,0:12:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.71,0:12:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会帮你喂它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.04,0:12:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你去帮团长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.88,0:12:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.78,0:12:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你来做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.35,0:12:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你打算又带特洛瓦去战斗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.69,0:12:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.06,0:12:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是我弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.72,0:12:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是这个马戏团的孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.33,0:12:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，他是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.79,0:12:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想让特洛瓦\N再有痛苦回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.93,0:12:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他没有记忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.80,0:12:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为那是痛苦的过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.30,0:12:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为他不想记起来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.60,0:12:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我…是我的错…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.47,0:12:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.81,0:12:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦为了纠正我犯的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.01,0:12:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才牺牲了自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.08,0:12:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然道歉不能弥补
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.15,0:12:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但真是对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.32,0:12:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若你那样想，你就别骚扰他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.45,0:12:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为和我们一起的现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.15,0:12:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦很幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.86,0:12:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起，特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.54,0:13:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个人是谁…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.51,0:13:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…认识他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.22,0:13:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我觉得好亲切…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.71,0:13:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拍档
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.64,0:13:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你会怎么办?还能战斗吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.28,0:13:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对啊，这样不像我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.82,0:13:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔见到特洛瓦了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.67,0:14:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凯萨琳，特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.41,0:14:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,观众的入场人数很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.11,0:14:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今日也要努力啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.28,0:14:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.74,0:14:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们会令观众一世都不会忘记
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.15,0:14:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对吧，特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.22,0:14:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.39,0:14:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.56,0:14:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.60,0:14:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交战中的OZ和白色獠牙部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.57,0:14:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正接近这空域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.13,0:14:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样下去\N这里也有可能被牵连
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.90,0:14:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.77,0:14:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里只有想平静生活的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.65,0:15:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶的OZ!竟然攻击卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.47,0:15:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家去疏散观众
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.60,0:15:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其他有空的就照顾动物们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.17,0:15:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.59,0:15:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你没事吧?特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.25,0:15:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好冷…好怕…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.89,0:15:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么会来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.66,0:15:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会有事，你放心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.43,0:15:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会陪着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.76,0:15:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.03,0:15:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.37,0:15:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.84,0:15:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里很危险，快去避难所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.38,0:16:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,究竟发生什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.38,0:16:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.88,0:16:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星附近爆发了机动战士对战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.32,0:16:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.59,0:16:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们只是想平静生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.42,0:16:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,究竟要有多少人\N牺牲才甘心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.60,0:16:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想再失去宝贵的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.60,0:16:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想再失去啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.47,0:16:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要哭，姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.01,0:16:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我会保护姐姐你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.28,0:16:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.55,0:16:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也已经不想再失去任何人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.79,0:16:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你救了我…救了我的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.26,0:16:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以，今次由我来保护大家啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.56,0:16:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹是为了那样才造出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.58,0:17:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!就此坚持到援军来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.06,0:17:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?援军吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.16,0:17:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是钢弹?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.86,0:17:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会再让你们伤害卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.22,0:17:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.96,0:17:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦，你要去哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.06,0:17:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人在呼唤我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.63,0:17:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎会有人呼唤你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.40,0:18:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道，那家伙在哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.14,0:18:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行啊!你遇过那么痛苦的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.14,0:18:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还打算继续战斗吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.75,0:18:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我记得从前有人这样说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.09,0:18:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遵照感情行事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.29,0:18:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是人类正确的生存方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.36,0:18:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你无论如何…都要去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.76,0:18:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为你固执的性格…毫无改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.87,0:18:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大笨蛋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.60,0:18:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定会活着回来啊，姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.84,0:18:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.25,0:18:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的是笨蛋吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.83,0:19:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定要令这种事结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.41,0:19:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.54,0:19:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.14,0:19:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下，你准备好了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.61,0:19:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,准备好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.28,0:19:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.55,0:19:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.92,0:20:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站在世界最高处\N的日子终于来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.85,0:20:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都很惊奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.39,0:20:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我高兴得感到同身受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.93,0:20:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.56,0:20:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的表情不可以那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.00,0:20:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要笑得更优雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.80,0:20:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为你从今日起\N就是世界的女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.62,0:20:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全世界的人请听我讲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.29,0:20:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是莉莉娜‧匹斯克拉福特  从今日起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.19,0:20:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成为罗姆斐拉财团的代表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.13,0:20:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，这并非为了罗姆斐拉财团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.27,0:20:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是为了令世界的纷争消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.54,0:20:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,建立和平的时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.97,0:20:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认为这是朝着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.54,0:20:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能和各位一起走的最好的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.74,0:21:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,踏出的第一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.31,0:21:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位，请你们抛掉武器\N停止斗争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.78,0:21:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位渴望的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.89,0:21:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该一定是相同的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.82,0:21:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我一起朝着那未来前进吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.83,0:21:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在这里宣布\N除去世界纷争之源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.56,0:21:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,国家的门户之见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.23,0:21:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,确立把地球当作一个国家的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.87,0:21:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[世界国家]宣言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.19,0:21:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也亏财团想得出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.26,0:21:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她的确能把人心\N吸向罗姆斐拉财团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.23,0:21:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，罗姆斐拉看来没发觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.36,0:21:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那会有很大的风险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.55,0:22:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.58,0:22:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.60,0:22:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心血来潮的找人出来\N只因为天气好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.60,0:22:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我一直等不到人\N你以为你是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.60,0:22:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你是跑过来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.60,0:22:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那也是应该的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.10,0:22:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love ! 那个惹人厌的人
